Turn On Lightning Article Editor and Article Personalization for Knowledge
Run the Lightning Knowledge Migration Tool

Get the latest Knowledge features when you migrate from Knowledge Classic to Lightning Knowledge. The Classic Knowledge data model retirement phase is in progress. To prepare for this retirement, run the Lightning Knowledge Migration Tool. After running the tool, you can still use Classic Knowledge in the Classic UI.

When: Salesforce enforces this update on June 1, 2025.
Who: This change applies to all Salesforce customers using Classic Knowledge.
Why: The Classic Knowledge data model is no longer available starting with Summer '25.

How: Run the Lightning Knowledge Migration Tool before the deadline to migrate to the Lightning Knowledge data model. After migration, you can still use Lightning Knowledge in Salesforce Classic, but some features are unavailable or behave differently.
